---
import Section from "../UI/Section.astro";
---

<Section id="for-business" title="Built for Businesses Ready to Scale" titleClassName="mb-8 text-balance">
	<p class="max-w-3xl text-center text-lg text-gray-200 text-pretty">
		YooCode is designed for organizations that need software to work the way their business actually operates.
	</p>

	<div class="mt-8 max-w-3xl w-full">
		<p class="text-base md:text-lg font-semibold text-white">If you&apos;re:</p>
		<ul class="mt-4 space-y-3 text-base md:text-lg text-gray-200 text-pretty list-disc list-inside">
			<li>Spending hours on repetitive tasks that could be automated</li>
			<li>Managing disconnected tools that don&apos;t integrate well</li>
			<li>Outgrowing off-the-shelf platforms</li>
			<li>Exploring AI, custom applications, or internal systems</li>
			<li>Lacking the internal engineering resources to build scalable solutions</li>
		</ul>
	</div>

	<p class="mt-8 max-w-3xl text-center text-lg md:text-xl text-white font-semibold text-pretty">
		Then custom software isn&apos;t a luxury, it&apos;s the next step.
	</p>
	<p class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-center text-base md:text-lg text-gray-200 text-pretty">
		Whether you&apos;re in Santa Rosa or operating nationally, YooCode builds systems that streamline operations, reduce friction, and support long-term growth.
	</p>
</Section>
